  "texts": [
    "The results obtained are the following.",
    "• XGB model has the highest R",
    "2 value of 0.932 and 0.937 in training and test phase.",
    "The DT, LR2 and SVR model showed good performance with R 2 value of 0.927 in training phase and 0.924, 0.924 and 0.923 in test phase respectively.",
    "While ANN, RR and LR1 showed lowest R 2 value of 0.62, 0.63 and 0.31 in training phase and 0.70, 0.56 and 0.40 in test phase respectively."
  ]
}